#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an9.22:7.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo assaparassā?"
msgstr "And what are the three excellent horses?"

msgctxt "an9.22:7.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco assaparasso … pe …"
msgstr "One excellent horse …"

msgctxt "an9.22:7.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca."
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned."

msgctxt "an9.22:7.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo assaparassā."
msgstr "These are the three excellent horses."

#. </p><p>
