msgctxt "an9.22:9.9"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, purisaparasso javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca "
"ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca."
msgstr "This is how an excellent person fast, beautiful, and well proportioned."

msgctxt "an9.22:9.10"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo purisaparassā."
msgstr "These are the three excellent people."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.400"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an9.22:10.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā assājānīyā?"
msgstr "And what are the three fine thoroughbred horses?"

msgctxt "an9.22:10.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco bhaddo assājānīyo … pe …"
msgstr "One fine thoroughbred horse …"

msgctxt "an9.22:10.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca."
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned."

msgctxt "an9.22:10.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā assājānīyā."
msgstr "These are the three fine thoroughbred horses."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an9.22:11.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā purisājānīyā?"
msgstr "And what are the three fine thoroughbred people?"

msgctxt "an9.22:11.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco bhaddo purisājānīyo … pe …"
msgstr "One fine thoroughbred person …"

msgctxt "an9.22:11.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca."
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an9.22:12.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhaddo purisājānīyo … pe …"
msgstr "And how is a fine thoroughbred person …"

msgctxt "an9.22:12.2"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca?"
msgstr "fast, beautiful, and well proportioned?"

msgctxt "an9.22:12.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"It’s a mendicant who realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by "
"wisdom in this very life. And they live having realized it with their own "
"insight due to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an9.22:12.4"
msgid "Idamassa javasmiṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "This is how they’re quick, I say."

msgctxt "an9.22:12.5"
msgid "Abhidhamme kho pana abhivinaye pañhaṃ puṭṭho vissajjeti, no saṃsādeti."
msgstr ""
"When asked a question about the teaching or training, they answer without "
"faltering."

msgctxt "an9.22:12.6"
msgid "Idamassa vaṇṇasmiṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "This is how they’re beautiful, I say."

msgctxt "an9.22:12.7"
msgid ""
"Lābhī kho pana hoti "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ."
